Here's what's going to happen next on THE BOLD AND THE 
BEAUTIFUL: 

Eric and Sally pull out all stops. Macy and Thorne talk things 
through. 

Here's what just happened on THE BOLD AND THE BEAUTIFUL:

Thomas feels left out as Ridge and Brooke bond with the girls. 
Later, Thomas sees the program for "The Portofino Challenge" 
which contains a tribute to Taylor. Thomas is touched by what
Brooke wrote about his mother. Ridge watches as Thomas allows 
Brooke to comfort him. Eric assures Brooke that he'll get rid 
of Deacon before anyone knows he's in Italy. Eric convinces 
Deacon to play things his way, contending that Brooke will 
never consider a life with Deacon if she's afraid of him. As 
Eric leads Deacon out, they run into Brooke and Ridge in the 
hall. Sally fumes as Stephanie courts the press, but when she 
confronts her, it's Sally who ends up all wet. Darla refuses 
to give away Macy's whereabouts, but agrees to pass a message 
along for Thorne. Darla is disappointed when she learns Macy 
intends on leaving Italy with Lorenzo and Adam. While Lorenzo 
and Adam are out making arrangements, Macy leaves for the 
church to meet with Thorne per Darla's instructions. When 
Deacon demands to speak with Brooke alone, Ridge and Deacon 
come to blows. Brooke gets Deacon to back down, and he 
reluctantly leaves with Eric. Brooke later discovers a 
heart-shaped doodle with her name on it in Deacon's hotel 
room, which she hides from Ridge. Bridget promises Stephanie 
she will keep Ridge's paternity a secret, but she's 
uncomfortable because she already feels a change in her 
relationship with Ridge. Lorenzo and Adam search for Macy. 
Macy arrives at the church and Thorne is overwhelmed with joy
at seeing her there. Last minute preparations are being nailed 
down as the fashion show gets underway. Ridge gives the 
Spectra gang a wonderful pep talk before the show begins. 
Brooke, Eric and Stephanie are happy to see Ridge acting like 
his old self again. Sally takes the stage with great fanfare 
and Ridge's first two fashions grace the runway.  

For the whole story of what happened last week, visit:
<a href="http://www.asthedialturns.com/boldandbeautiful.htm">
The Bold & The Beautiful</a>
http://www.asthedialturns.com/boldandbeautiful.htm

